""""""""""Aesthetics
colorscheme vimPgray

"Change link UI ("Hints")
:highlight Hint font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: white; background-color: green; border-color: ButtonShadow; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; padding: 0px 1px 0px 1px;


""""""""""Bindings
"Scrolling
:noremap j 5j
:noremap k 5k
:noremap J <C-d>
:noremap K <C-u>

"control-a selects all in insert mode
:inoremap <C-a> <Ins><C-a><Ins>

"private window
:map <C-S-n> :winopen<Space>-private<Return>

"Add dictionary to alt-shift-d
:map <A-S-d> :open http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/


""""""""""Quickmarks
:qmark o www.outlook.com/owa/microsoft.com
:qmark g www.gmail.com
:qmark s www.stackoverflow.com


""""""""""Misc
"Set startpage.com as the default search when using :open/:tabopen
:set defsearch=startpage

"tab numbers (#gt)
:set tabnumbers

"have to press enter before going to link
:set followhints=1

"use chars instead of the silly number system
:set hintchars=asdfjkl

"visual bell
:set visualbell
